content: I've been doing a lot of research on plant-based diets lately, and I've been experimenting with different recipes and ingredients. By the way, I've been a lacto-ovo vegetarian for about 6 months now, and I've been dabbling in vegan cooking for the past 3 months. It's been a game-changer for my health and the environment. Anyway, back to protein powders... Do you have any recommendations for a good vegan protein powder that's also low in carbs?
